text: The River Teme is a river in England and Wales. Teme may also refer to: ==Rivers== * Teme River, New Zealand ==Other uses== * Teme (philosophy), a term meaning technological meme *Teme language, a language of Nigeria * True Equator, Mean Equinox frame used in the Earth-centered inertial coordinate system ==See also== * *Temes (disambiguation)
title: Teme (disambiguation)
